1. Juče sam kupila novu knjigu u radnji. (*radnji*) (Yesterday I bought a new book in the store.)
2. Moramo da obavimo važnu radnju pre nego što odemo. (*radnju*) (We have to do an important task before we leave.)
3. Ulica u kojoj se nalazi radnja je veoma prometna. (*radnja*) (The street where the shop is located is very busy.)
4. Ona je veoma posvećena svojoj radnji. (*radnji*) (She is very dedicated to her business.)
5. Molim vas da završite tu radnju do kraja dana. (*radnju*) (Please finish that task by the end of the day.)
6. Sinoć smo imali pljačku u radnji. (*radnji*) (Last night we had a robbery in the store.)
7. Radnja je bila zatvorena zbog renoviranja. (*radnja*) (The shop was closed due to renovation.)
8. Prošle godine sam u ovoj radnji kupio poklon za sestru. (*radnji*) (Last year I bought a gift for my sister in this shop.)
9. Nisam siguran gde se ta radnja tačno nalazi. (*radnja*) (I'm not sure where exactly that shop is located.)
10. Sutra ćemo otvoriti novu radnju u gradu. (*radnju*) (Tomorrow we will open a new store in the city.)